    "major_stream_name": "Science",
    "like_dislike_summary": {
      "pos_sentences": [
        {
          "text": "I have enjoyed my college life very well with my friends and teachers who have always motivated me to move ahead in my life.",
          "name": "Pranjal tiwari",
          "course_tag_name": "BCA"
        },
        {
          "text": "There are many activities in my campus like I participated in volleyball, kabaddi, cricket but this was physical. There are many fests in our college which we consider as annual functions.",
          "name": "Pranjal tiwari",
          "course_tag_name": "BCA"
        },
        {
          "text": "Holkar Science College is very good anyway, it has also got A++ from NACC, so I don't think that there is any need to improve anything in the college",
          "name": "Pranjal tiwari",
          "course_tag_name": "BCA"
        },
        {
          "text": "The labs here were amazing, in which all kinds of necessary things were done so that the children could do practical work well.",
          "name": "Rana pratap Pathak",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Sc"
        },
        {
          "text": "The most beautiful thing about this college was that there were a lot of trees and plants here",
          "name": "Rana pratap Pathak",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Sc"
        },
        {
          "text": "my college location was in the middle of city.at the walking distance.",
          "name": "Deepanshu",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Sc"
        },
        {
          "text": "My college  campus,was lush green,pollution free,and healthy environment.",
          "name": "Deepanshu",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Sc"
        },
        {
          "text": "My college teaching faculties was highly qualified and helpful. Almost all faculties were Phd.",
          "name": "Deepanshu",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Sc"
        },
        {
          "text": "There is availability of good infrastructure and computer classes also",
          "name": "Prashant choure",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Sc"
        },
        {
          "text": "The environment of our college is so lovable at there is a lot of greenery present there",
          "name": "Prashant choure",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Sc"
        }
      ],
      "neg_sentences": [
        {
          "text": "Their negative point is thier infrastructure is poor and most of the buildings is old but thier maintenance is too good because this college is the existing to the time of British rules",
          "name": "Rahul Meena",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Sc"
        },
        {
          "text": "air conditioners are always switch offed.",
          "name": "Kunal harinkhede",
          "course_tag_name": "BCA"
        },
        {
          "text": "A dislike thing in my college is cannot give any placement",
          "name": "Pranjal tiwari",
          "course_tag_name": "BCA"
        },
        {
          "text": "Holkar Science College library is considered to be the biggest library of Madhya Pradesh, but many times it became very difficult to get books from there.",
          "name": "Rana pratap Pathak",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Sc"
        },
        {
          "text": "Students were not allowed to go to the 3 gardens here. I feel that if the gardens were made for students, then they should have been given permission to go there.",
          "name": "Rana pratap Pathak",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Sc"
        },
        {
          "text": "my college was 135 years old so infrastructure in some classes was old.",
          "name": "Deepanshu",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Sc"
        },
        {
          "text": "At the time of our classes there is a lot of building works going on that is also frustrated me",
          "name": "Prashant choure",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Sc"
        },
        {
          "text": "The thing that is very frustrating for me is the online website where I have to get my admit card and exam notification",
          "name": "Prashant choure",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Sc"
        }
      ]
    },
    "affiliated_to": {
      "name": "Devi Ahilya Vishwavidyalaya Indore, Indore"
    }
  },
